# pegase1354_fdia_pipeline.py
# End-to-end FDIA pipeline on IEEE 1354-PEGASE using ONLY pandapower's built-in network.
# Steps (via CLI flags):
#   --make-csv    : generate pegase1354_timeseries.csv
#   --run-pf      : time-series AC power flow driven by the CSV
#   --run-ukf     : UKF + anomaly detection (IF + HistGB)
#   --plot-panels : show χ²/IF/HGB for one simulation id
#   --plot-trace  : show |V| and θ for one bus in the chosen substation

